reviewText: This video fits in current context well as the gov't continues to examine the worth of producing pennies. A penny for your thoughts takes on new meaning for sure as the cost of its production exceeds it value. Unbiased reviews from both "for" and "against" constituents shapes the presented information. One is left to wonder (by following news releases currently) what is holding up a decision -- to be or not to be... that is the penny's question.
